    {
      "id": "93",
      "name": "Lore",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Elynas's Birth",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Before he was born, Elynas floated in the cosmic darkness in cold and loneliness. He was so sad, so he would often cry. Later he heard Mother's voice, who wished for Elynas to be born into a beautiful world. She gave him life, a strong and healthy body that could walk the world, and a beautiful name. She wanted to give him many siblings, to meet many friends, and to see the beautiful sights beyond that cosmic dark. Elynas and his siblings loved and cared for each other.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Later, Elynas along with his siblings left the world beneath the earth. He felt the wind brushing against his skin, the warmth of the sun, waters icy and warm. At first, Elynas was happy, but he soon discovered that what seemed interesting and funny to him was scary and dangerous for others. He learned that his blood was poisoned and that he was bringing suffering and destruction to the people of Teyvat, but it was too late.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Judging by the fact that Elynas blood is similar in composition to the Shadow Dragon Durin’s blood, that they both referred to the creator as Mother and they both have the same goal when they entered Teyvat, it can be assumed that Elynas and Durin have the same creator — the alchemist Rhinedottir, also known as Gold. She is the mother of Durin, Albedo and many other Abyssal beasts, and also one of the reasons for the Cataclysm.",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Related Entries:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 6368,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Rhinedottir",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4903,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Дурин",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 47,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Albedo_icon.png",
                      "name": "Альбедо",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
